Map includes:

*Shot For Shot
*Knife area
*Chicken Fight
*Vents-Network ( Fixed + bigger )
*Secret ways ( Many secret ways )
*Fixed Plants
*Fixed light
*Glass Room ( Secret Room(s))
And more!

The map is called ProfessorOaks Office, that's why the theme is actually the same as: cs_office.

So there are no special rooms, for example: for gun toss.
It's all made-in the map.

Enjoy & Comment something ( BTW: This is the first map i've ever made ;P )
